{"tid":1775101,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［非分化］你地可摸耳咪再咁「惡」？","createTime":"2019-12-08T15:40:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-08T17:24:44.000Z","uid":245759,"like":57,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7485b6e38e80441bd857cbd7578784c67c275d4d","tid":1775101,"uid":245759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:40:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 可摸耳咪撚再屌人影相？？？</span><br />\n真係見到條友影人大頭除外啦 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">出得黎行 包實自己係自己既責任 </span></span><br />\n啲老友記影下景 打下卡 <br />\n啲遊客影下我地 幫我地國際文宣下 <br />\n就比我地鬧到一面屁 其實佢地好多都係自己友黎架<br />\n佢地要影個啲咪溫柔小小提醒下佢地<br />\n可摸耳咪再咁「惡」？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2. 可摸耳咪撚再撚狗？？？</span><br />\n你都知啲狗既脾氣幾差 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你係前面搞啲狗 之後就其他手足受氣</span></span><br />\n一撚狗就嗌得最大聲 一出tg個啲就跑得最快 <br />\n係咪覺得自己撚狗好撚型先？聲大夾惡好威？<br />\n可唔可以冷靜ddddd呀？<br />\n<br />\n善意提醒 下次可摸耳咪再咁「惡」呀？<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"b18d843306180970d74f8af0c31467ce1dfe691b","tid":1775101,"uid":322261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:43:36.000Z","msg":"摸耳"},{"pid":"226022fd8904572f9879eb38090ff9d4f0c25852","tid":1775101,"uid":245759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:54:50.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"163493047f1550f517d38ade01e3dc76932a6bd4","tid":1775101,"uid":245759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:55:02.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9ea47ba517b210165a39cd847c6dfa7baea0103","tid":1775101,"uid":245759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-08T15:55:27.000Z","msg":"push<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a171b370389ab70a327509a5cb07601e724c9e6e","tid":1775101,"uid":66730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-